OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatchy fog and frost will soon
OL,6,Fclear to leave some dry weather this
OL,7,Fmorning with sunny spells. However,
OL,8,Fcloud will gradually increase and a
OL,9,Fscattering of showers are likely to
OL,10,Fdevelop by the afternoon. A gentle
OL,11,Feasterly breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThere will be clear spells at
OL,14,Ftimes during the evening and
OL,15,Fovernight. However, further showers
OL,16,Fare also expected. The easterly wind
OL,17,Fwill freshen, though a patchy frost is
OL,18,Fstill expected.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,166,160,301,260,100,100
