OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FTuesday morning will see
OL,6,Fbright spells and a scattering of
OL,7,Fshowers. It should become mostly dry
OL,8,Fin the afternoon though with pleasant
OL,9,Fspells of sunshine. Feeling cooler in
OL,10,Fthe wind.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FLargely dry during the remainder of
OL,14,Fthe week, with high pressure giving
OL,15,Fgenerally settled weather. Some warm
OL,16,Fsunshine, though breezy at first, and
OL,17,Fsome patchy overnight frosts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
